[
    {
        "content": "<p>Is there a better way to get a <code>(name, globs)</code> list than to run <code>lake translate-config toml</code> and reading the resulting toml file?</p>",
        "id": 503386594,
        "sender_full_name": "Eric Wieser",
        "timestamp": 1741131690
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><code>getLeanLibs</code> from <code>scripts/mk_all.lean</code> gets close to this, right?</p>",
        "id": 503388953,
        "sender_full_name": "Damiano Testa",
        "timestamp": 1741132807
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>E.g., for mathlib, I get</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"sd\">/-- info: #[Mathlib, Archive, Counterexamples, docs, Mathlib/Tactic] -/</span>\n<span class=\"bp\">#</span><span class=\"n\">guard_msgs</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">in</span>\n<span class=\"bp\">#</span><span class=\"n\">eval</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">do</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">dbg_trace</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">getLeanLibs</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 503389272,
        "sender_full_name": "Damiano Testa",
        "timestamp": 1741132916
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Thanks, I knew we had an example of that somewhere!</p>",
        "id": 503389969,
        "sender_full_name": "Eric Wieser",
        "timestamp": 1741133217
    },
    {
        "content": "<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">open</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Lean</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">System</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">FilePath</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">open</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Lake</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">in</span>\n<span class=\"sd\">/-- `getLeanLibs` returns the names (as an `Array` of `String`s) of all the libraries</span>\n<span class=\"sd\">on which the current project depends.</span>\n<span class=\"sd\">If the current project is `mathlib`, then it excludes the libraries `Cache` and `LongestPole` and</span>\n<span class=\"sd\">it includes `Mathlib/Tactic`. -/</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">getLeanLibs</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">IO</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Array</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">String</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">×</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Array</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">String</span><span class=\"o\">))</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">do</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">elanInstall?</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">leanInstall?</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">lakeInstall?</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">findInstall?</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">config</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">MonadError</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">runEIO</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">&lt;|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">mkLoadConfig</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">elanInstall?</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">leanInstall?</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">lakeInstall?</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">}</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">some</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ws</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">loadWorkspace</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">config</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">|&gt;.</span><span class=\"n\">toBaseIO</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">throw</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">&lt;|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">IO</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">userError</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"failed to load Lake workspace\"</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">package</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ws</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">root</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">libs</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">package</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">leanLibs</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">map</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">·.</span><span class=\"n\">name</span><span class=\"o\">))</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">map</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">·.</span><span class=\"n\">toString</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">globs</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">package</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">leanLibs</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">map</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">·.</span><span class=\"n\">config</span><span class=\"o\">))</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">map</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">·.</span><span class=\"n\">globs</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">libsGlobs</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">libs</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">zip</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">globs</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">return</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">libsGlobs</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">map</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">fun</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">g</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">g</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">map</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">·.</span><span class=\"n\">toString</span><span class=\"o\">))</span>\n\n<span class=\"sd\">/--</span>\n<span class=\"sd\">info: #[(Mathlib, #[Mathlib]), (Cache, #[Cache]), (LongestPole, #[LongestPole]), (MathlibTest, #[MathlibTest.+]), (Archive, #[Archive]), (Counterexamples, #[Counterexamples]), (docs, #[docs])]</span>\n<span class=\"sd\">-/</span>\n<span class=\"bp\">#</span><span class=\"n\">guard_msgs</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">in</span>\n<span class=\"bp\">#</span><span class=\"n\">eval</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">do</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">dbg_trace</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">getLeanLibs</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 503390289,
        "sender_full_name": "Damiano Testa",
        "timestamp": 1741133364
    },
